Coroebus
========

A C++ client library for Apache Cassandra

Installation
============

    ./config/autorun.sh
    ./configure
    make 
    make install

Running Unit Tests
==================

The tests require gtest to be installed and Cassandra to be
running with the default cassandra.yaml.

    make check

Compiling Against Coroebus
==========================

    g++ file.cc -lcoroebus -lthrift -I/usr/local/include/thfit

Modify the include with the actual location of your Thrift headers.
